{"tid":1923236,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"光時 可唔可以做買 黃店飲食券平台","createTime":"2020-03-13T03:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T05:30:52.000Z","uid":143151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3989b4407146ecfe1b332d1c909250edad25d518","tid":1923236,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:18:07.000Z","msg":"例如邀請黃店整啲95折 9折現金券<br />\n放係你哋平台到賣 你哋收翻少少佣咁<br />\n<br />\n第一 增加黃店現金流<br />\n我哋買咗啲現金券 可以備用<br />\n呢排未必成日出去食飯 少咗支持黃店機會<br />\n成日擔心黃店做唔住<br />\n如果有得買券 遲啲食 至少可以維持佢哋現金收入<br />\n<br />\n第二 增加用戶量<br />\n單靠賣零食乾糧 未必吸引到大部份人用呢個平台<br />\n因為競爭力同HKtvmall 百佳 759 <br />\n係方便 同 種類 仲有一段落差<br />\n但食券唔係周圍有得買<br />\n可以吸引新顧客加入<br />\n<br />\n第三 增加光時收入<br />\n每單可能抽1至2%<br />\n積少成多都好<br />\n唔洗有入貨成本 都物流問題<br />\n可以直接e-coupon 俾客人<br />\n<br />\n第四 吸引支持者 試新黃店<br />\n睇到唔同promotion 可能加大吸引力<br />\n同埋可以explore 到更多黃店<br />\n<br />\n雖然明白要整 應該唔係一兩日嘅事<br />\n不過希望光時 認真考慮下<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"4567dd84bfaf760cd2a36ea073d082b5fd314540","tid":1923236,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得諗 發大黎做 黃店可以做埋貨物自取點<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都一齊做大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac6d6975d5128e6865f593b5d7b32d1ed46977d","tid":1923236,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4567dd84bfaf760cd2a36ea073d082b5fd314540","tid":1923236,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得諗 發大黎做 黃店可以做埋貨物自取點<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都一齊做大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:27:00.000Z","msg":"畢竟飲食業 現金流好重要<br />\n至少告急前 我哋可以bump下水俾佢頂住先<br />\n日日睇住黃店告急 心痛<br />\n同埋見光時貨品有啲少 <br />\n咁做 應該吸引多啲人用"},{"pid":"2dafe9fad3ffb6fa2f33266d3a0a619f1b375d66","tid":1923236,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"創意台 係咪冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193584a32e8e78cd2e062d74a79939e80139237b","tid":1923236,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"1d9cc720d7c127594ba5473c05570e35c0edeb39","tid":1923236,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dafe9fad3ffb6fa2f33266d3a0a619f1b375d66","tid":1923236,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"創意台 係咪冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開係創意台真係無乜人睇 不如直接開時事台啦"},{"pid":"8c1a987ab18fb889b7015f055ed17e2e7a3a4871","tid":1923236,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"開時事台啦<br />\n或者inbox光時啦"},{"pid":"ad9b4333a8296045cf60a4d3bfb180251d156b65","tid":1923236,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c1a987ab18fb889b7015f055ed17e2e7a3a4871","tid":1923236,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"開時事台啦<br />\n或者inbox光時啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bbb3917c68c14594909e6164e4b7f9afdbfca160","tid":1923236,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20